spec:
add circleci config to the module to allow git to kick off a build when commits are pushed to main
as the end of the build the artefacts should then be published to jitpack
commitMessage:
Add CircleCI configuration for CI/CD with JitPack integration

- Added CircleCI config to build and test on all branches
- Added publish job that runs only on the main branch
- Updated JitPack configuration to work with CircleCI
- Added CI/CD information to README
- Modified build.gradle.kts to handle JitPack environment
